Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.45,0:00:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything \Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.42,0:00:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything this \Nworld has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone is in search of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:26.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:30.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jitto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:30.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:34.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:34.84,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:40.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:40.05,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly the flag, Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:45.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,hata wo ageyou Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:45.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,namikaze tateyou suriipu kara no janpusutaato
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:50.85,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make waves, jump from your sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:50.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,arienai sekai wo iku nara
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:55.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go to the unbelievable world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:00:55.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kimi no tafunesu sore ga hitsuyou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:01:00.07,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,your toughness, that’s what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:00.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,medachisugi sorette tsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:02.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Being brazen, is it a crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:02.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shimeitehai->tsumari Winner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:05.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanted->means Winner:D
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:05.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jiyuu dakega ore tachi no ruuru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:11.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom is our only rule
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:11.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinpai nante dokofuku kaze--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:16.88,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not our way to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:16.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ttai one piece ichibannori
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:19.42,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,At any cost, One Piece, I’ll be the first
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:19.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume miru kokoro wa choo dekai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:23.51,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,My dreaming heart is huge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:23.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,samenai koto ga daiji--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:27.81,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s important not to wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:27.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:30.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:30.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:34.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:34.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:39.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:39.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa...koko made kitaze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:45.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We...made it this far
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:45.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa iku...yume no arika e
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:48.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We go...to where the dream is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:48.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dare mo oitekanaize--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:53.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t left anyone behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:53.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nshin aru nomi sore ga chikai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:56.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going forward, that’s our pledge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:01:56.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume ga hajimatta ano hi kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:02:00.55,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the day that the dream began
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:00.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,mezasu mirai wa onaji--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:04.63,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,the future that I’m \Naiming at hasn’t changed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:04.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:07.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:07.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kokoro no taiyou shizumanai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:11.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun of my heart will never set
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:11.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:15.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:15.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:19.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:19.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:27.75,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:32.62,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.64,0:02:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.10,0:02:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, \Nthe second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.32,0:02:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.32,0:02:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.03,0:02:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:02:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.21,0:03:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his crew reached the Fish-Man \NIsland located 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.92,0:03:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where the New Fish-Man Pirates who are \Nlooking to destroy the Ryugu Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...assisted by Vander Decken, who is after\NShirahoshi, are engaging in secret maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats find themselves\N caught up in the turmoil
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.81,0:03:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Zoro, Usopp and Brook got \Ncaught by Hordy at the Ryugu Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go to the Ryugu Palace to save\N my crew and kick that Hordy guy's ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.44,0:03:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said "Don't do it"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:36.15,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Something Has Happened to Hordy!\N The True Power of the Evil Drug!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.87,0:03:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for the decisive battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as soon as we cut the King's head off,\N the morale of his army will be shattered
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then it's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means we'll have a new king soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:04:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, at Candy Factory \NTown in the center of the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:14.73,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1000)}CANDY FACTORY
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daruma-san, w-what are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.08,0:04:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He's chewing the wall of the factory...\N--W-What powerful jaws!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My fangs itch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.15,0:04:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.40,0:04:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want some trendy cappuccino\N and cake for my happy snack time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.95,0:04:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look like a yuppie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry, Daruma-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to bite your flesh off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:05:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My favorite snack is the bones of \Nbig fish! And don't ever forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.33,0:05:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, I'll be careful from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.04,0:05:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. I'm gonna go chew up the \Nroyal family and their soldiers now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you at Conchcorde Plaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.35,0:05:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all have to be there! Don't be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do about the citizens?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you listening to what Boss said?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said "No more stepping on her picture."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave them alone! \NThey know what's waiting for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New Fish-Man Pirates have...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...4 shark Fish-Man officers including Hordy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and 1 giant squid Fish-Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.89,0:06:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, they have a blue-ringed \Noctopus Merman as a bodyguard,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.93,0:06:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who is the best swordsman on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.60,0:06:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our only hope is the Neptune brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.69,0:06:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in the Princes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.86,0:06:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotsun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.11,0:06:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At Waterwheel Town in \Nthe north of the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.11,0:06:19.76,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1000)}WATERWHEEL TOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The Princes are heading to Conchcorde Plaza!\N--What's gonna happen to this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. All we wanted was \Nfriendly relations with humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should our lives be threatened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe they're \Ngonna execute the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we stop them by taking\N these guys as hostages?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hostages?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not gonna work. \NBoss Hordy is a ruthless man-kotsun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.73,0:06:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you try it, he'll just cut \Nus off and go on as planned-kotsun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:07:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not good. Because he \Ngot beaten by the Princes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dosun-san's power level\N went down to "kotsun."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.62,0:07:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He needs the Energy Steroid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always been like that-kotsun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has too much pride-potsun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Potsun"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.68,0:07:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't like Fish-Men who do \Nbusiness with human pirates-posun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Posun"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.86,0:07:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those Fish-Men who transfused\N blood to wounded humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he punished them by attacking\N them in the dark-tosun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Tosun"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans' blood is tainted-tosun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both giving them blood \Nand getting their blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...degrades our Fish-Man blood-dosun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.67,0:07:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's back to "dosun"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:08:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those Fish-Men who support\N the horrible humans are...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.14,0:08:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...getting in the way of...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Our noble intentions-dokan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He exceeded "dosun"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He broke the chain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.19,0:08:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The soldiers got blown away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Fukaboshi! \NI'll get even with you-bokan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat you to within an inch \Nof your life next time-zugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, guys-bagon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.02,0:08:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Conchcorde Plaza, \Nthe execution ground-gaban!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.27,0:08:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In front of the Fish-Man Cultural\N Hall in the south of the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.27,0:09:04.27,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1000)}FISH-MAN CULTURAL HALL
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did you say is drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.62,0:09:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are, Hyouzou-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.70,0:09:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get yourself back together!\N You can't fight like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.37,0:09:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No worries, no worries! This is my treat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to fight Neptune's army \Nwhich is being led by Fukaboshi now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the worst-case scenario, \Nthe infamous Jimbei will be there too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stand on your feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good. He's as \Nslippery as a sea cucumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe how many degrees\N your head can spin around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not spinning! You're too drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy! I bet you can't even hold your sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.99,0:09:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stay away from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouzou will slice into \Nanyone when he gets drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:10:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He will... slice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sliced his friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.12,0:10:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna cut more!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.42,0:10:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hyouzou-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to the plaza now and slice up the \NNeptunes to your heart's content!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.81,0:10:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oiaiyonohoniaiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.93,0:10:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:10:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the Marine Shopping Mall\N in the east of the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:03.67,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1000)}MARINE SHOPPING MALL
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.69,0:11:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're former soldiers of Neptune's army!\N We won't let you do whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! He disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.67,0:11:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He disappeared again! How can he do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you civilians do now? Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeo-san can change his skin color like\N a chameleon and camouflage himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.44,0:11:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's even hard for us to \Nfigure out where he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's impossible for \Nus to beat a guy like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your only hope is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.62,0:12:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Neptune brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.46,0:12:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they'll die soon just like the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.17,0:12:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means you folk have...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.82,0:12:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened? He stopped talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.44,0:12:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the cockroach dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's flattened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.33,0:12:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Which means you folk have nowhere to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nowhere to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He kept his nobility! He's not known as the \NNoble of the Fish-Man District for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.59,0:12:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he pretending as if nothing happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.51,0:12:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.47,0:13:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later today, at Conchcorde Plaza,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Neptune family will die\N and the new king will rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go to the plaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.78,0:13:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hordy! Wh-What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's nothing.\N--But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, bring it to me now! As much as we have!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.50,0:13:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.84,0:13:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better not take more Energy Steroid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.89,0:13:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want your head to \Nget smashed?! Just shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.06,0:13:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! We got King Neptune already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Victory is within our grasp!\N So you don't have to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right! Don't push yourself too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm running out of time! \NI said "Get out of my way"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.19,0:14:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't! I said "Leave it up to me"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.69,0:14:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you understand \Neven after I've explained it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a damn about the history\N between Fish-Men and humans
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when my friends are in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why! That is why I want you to wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They both wanna help the \Ncountry and their friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.72,0:15:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do they have to fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.64,0:15:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long will it take to Conchcorde Plaza?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.64,0:15:05.58,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1000)}"WATERWHEEL TOWN" TO "CONCHCORDE PLAZA"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Less than an hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the actions of a sane \Nman to go through the trouble of
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.69,0:15:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,executing the King at the plaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.36,0:15:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think they just wanna lure you Princes out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.03,0:15:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am looking forward to it, rather.\N I won't let them hurt my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.24,0:15:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I won't let our people's minds close again,\N not after they were just opening up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I know why Jimbei \Nalways had his eyes on Hordy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.71,0:15:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they are the reason we haven't seen \Nhuman pirates around the island these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Shirahoshi is \Nstill in the Hard Shell Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help worrying because we don't \Nhear anything about her-fa-so-la-ti-do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Fukaboshi-sama, \Nwhat do you think about the Straw Hats?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.27,0:15:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Sharley said they \Nwill destroy this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:16:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They did not seem like they had bad intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat is Jimbei's friend and the Mermaids\N at the cove didn't speak badly of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those Mermaids sure have an eye for people!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is not the time to \Nthink about those things!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right-la-ti-do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon all soldiers from all over the country!\N We will save the King at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.05,0:16:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At Fishverly Hills in the \Nnortheast of the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:34.27,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1000)}FISHVERLY HILLS
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.57,0:16:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that we are still \Nstruggling against just one sea monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is something not \Nright with this sea monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.12,0:16:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn fools, it serves \Nyou right! Good job, Sea Bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.04,0:16:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Energy Steroid worked too well!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:17:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Calm down, Sea Bear! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those soldiers are barely alive.\N So it's over, Sea Bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use this! Sea monsters don't like fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Much?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ikaros-san's body is contorting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it some kind of curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.66,0:17:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put out the fire-ch, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.04,0:17:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crackle, crackle...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.96,0:17:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire? What about the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become a piece of dried squid-ch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.17,0:17:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.35,0:17:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you were trying to roast me and\N eat me with sake. I'll kill you-ch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would do that, fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.52,0:17:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.48,0:18:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ikaros-san once had a best \Nfriend who was a giant squid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, he went too close to the sun\N and became a giant dried squid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why when Ikaros-san sees fire, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daidalos!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.91,0:18:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a Fish-Man. He's not \Ngonna be like his friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daida...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful hereafter-ch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.14,0:18:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Dried Squid Spear is always waiting for\N its chance to turn back into a normal squid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.47,0:18:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So once it gets stuck in someone,\N it'll suck all fluid out of his body!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.90,0:18:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ika!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ika, Ika, Ika, Ika, Ika, Ika, Ika...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.65,0:18:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's awful! \NHe's pummeling that guy who got dried out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ikaros-san, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.20,0:18:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't we have to go to the plaza already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.87,0:18:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Much! You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.54,0:19:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late. \NHe already became a dried squid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minister of the Right! Look up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Hordy and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.09,0:19:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see Hordy but I see some \Nmen from the Fish-Man District!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're heading to the plaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, those bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.89,0:19:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! The King-sama is on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Neptune-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.86,0:19:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great Knight, perform a miracle to save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.11,0:19:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me Great Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.91,0:19:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't save my citizens--look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.87,0:19:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.12,0:19:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the King's army but we \Ncan't even protect the King?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.92,0:19:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what are we here for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.92,0:19:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ikaros-san! There are only 2 \Nhours left until the execution!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.84,0:19:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with us to Conchcorde Plaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Captain Hordy-ch?!\N I know he's there-ch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.85,0:19:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't he even come out-ch?! Much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.89,0:20:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.48,0:20:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That drug enhances your strength\N but takes years off your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't take it in \Nthe first place-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.32,0:20:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hordy said he got cut by \Nthe pirate swordsman and it hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut? The Boss got cut?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he kept taking the Energy\N Steroid to kill the pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.80,0:20:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he ended up... I mean, \Nwe told him to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.27,0:20:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hordy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.48,0:20:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't... breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.56,0:20:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body is gonna explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.19,0:20:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Much! Is it a side-effect-ch?! So that \Ndrug could kill you as I thought-ch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.32,0:21:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.08,0:21:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong, Sea Bear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.42,0:21:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's acting strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.05,0:21:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although all these sea monsters \Nare under Captain Hordy's control,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.59,0:22:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen them get so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.10,0:22:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--C-Captain Hordy?!\N--Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.15,0:22:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why shouldn't I be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.28,0:22:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hordy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.71,0:22:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see some soldiers from the army!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.13,0:22:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.04,0:23:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Facing the destructive power of Hordy's new form,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.59,0:23:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neptune's army is defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.47,0:23:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The citizens have only one hope remaining...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.47,0:23:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three Neptune brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.22,0:23:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They rise to face Hordy, and their battle begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.27,0:23:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.52,0:23:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Battle is on!\NAt Conchcorde Plaza!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.44,0:23:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
